tors like the Einstein Telescope can seize the GW\nsignals from these sources in the future.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Aug 2020 03:39:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 20 Aug 2020 15:57:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-25"}
