le layer\nCrPS4. The current structural and optical investigation will provide a firm\nbasis for future study and application of this novel magnetic semiconductor.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Aug 2020 05:56:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-07"}
