ly a universal formation\nmechanism and evolutionary history for SX Phoenicis stars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Aug 2020 09:39:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 20 Aug 2020 11:14:12 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 18 Nov 2020 09:22:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-19"}
